OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FGenerally
OL,6,Fdry and initially clear conditions
OL,7,Facross the region. Some patchy cloud
OL,8,Flikely to spread from the north
OL,9,Fovernight but still with some clear
OL,10,Fspells. Winds will ease to become
OL,11,Flight for most.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FGenerally dry with bright
OL,14,Fspells, although rather cloudier at
OL,15,Ftimes, more especially toward the
OL,16,Fnorth of the region. Mostly light
OL,17,Fwinds, and feeling rather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
